li.media
  .media-left
    = gravatar_tag activity.owner, class: 'media-object img-circle'
  .media-body
    p.media-heading
      strong
        = link_to activity.owner.nickname, activity.owner
        small.text-muted
          span.name<
            | @#{activity.owner.name}
          span.time<
            = time_ago_in_words activity.created_at
    p
      | 『
      = link_to_if activity.trackable, activity.parameters[:title], [activity.owner, activity.trackable]
      | 』を編集しました。
